  "industry_note": "JIS spring steels (G4801): SUP9 (UNS G51500 / 51CrV4 / DIN 1.7176 / KS SUP9 — Cr-Mn 51 series, C 0.52-0.60, Mn 0.65-0.95, Cr 0.65-0.95) vs SUP10 (51CrV4 / DIN 1.8159 / KS SUP10 — Cr-V, C 0.47-0.55, Cr 0.80-1.10, V 0.15+). Q+T 380°C (full spring): σy +100/UTS +100. Tmax 480°C (over-tempering 위). 자동차 leaf spring (truck), coil spring (valve), torsion bar. 한국 SUP9, SUP10 도 동일.",
